api_list.name: BETS/LİST
api_list.description: The program that analyzes the past matches and predicts the match predictions by 90% thanks to the algorithm.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://livescore19.p.rapidapi.com/bet/list"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "livescore19.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
